 people of prayer will be called from the gate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14331,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/jihad-helping-defenders\/","url_meta":{"origin":8016,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Supporting those who defend the Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Khalid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever equips a soldier in the way of Allah, or who cares for the family of a soldier in the way of Allah, he will receive the reward as if he went into battle himself.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/worship-jihad-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":8016,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet strives in last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the last ten nights of Ramadan arrived, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would tighten his belt, spend the night in worship, and awaken his family. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2024, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1174 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629